'''大取代'''（{{lang-fr|Grand Remplacement}}），抑或称'''取代理论'''<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Bracke|first1=Sarah|last2=Aguilar|first2=Luis Manuel Hernández|year=2020|title='They love death as we love life': The 'Muslim Question' and the biopolitics of replacement|journal=The British Journal of Sociology|volume=71|issue=4|pages=680–701|doi=10.1111/1468-4446.12742|pmid=32100887|pmc=7540673|issn=1468-4446|doi-access=free}}</ref><ref name="Bowles">{{cite news |last=Bowles |first=Nellie |title='Replacement Theory,' a Racist, Sexist Doctrine, Spreads in Far-Right Circles |work=The New York Times |date=2019-03-18 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/18/technology/replacement-theory.html |quote=Behind the idea is a racist conspiracy theory known as 'the replacement theory,' which was popularized by a right-wing French philosopher. |access-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517014150/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/18/technology/replacement-theory.html |archive-date=2019-05-17 |url-status=live }}</ref>，是[[白人民族主义|白人民族主义者]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Feola|first=Michael|year=2020|title='You Will Not Replace Us': The Melancholic Nationalism of Whiteness|journal=Political Theory|volume=49|issue=4|pages=528–553|doi=10.1177/0090591720972745|issn=0090-5917|quote=This article addresses recent strains of white nationalism rooted within anxieties over demographic replacement (e.g., "the Great Replacement").|doi-access=free}}</ref>提倡的[[极右派|极右]][[阴谋论|阴谋论]]<ref name="taguieff71">{{Harvp|Taguieff|2015}}, [https://books.google.com/books?id=guYJCwAAQBAJ&pg=PT71 PT71] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=guYJCwAAQBAJ&pg=PT71 |date=20201029043810 }}.</ref><ref name="Baldauf 2017">{{cite book|url=https://www.amadeu-antonio-stiftung.de/w/files/englisch/monitoring-2017-englisch-int.pdf|title=Toxische Narrative : Monitoring rechts-alternativer Akteure|publisher=Amadeu Antonio Stiftung|year=2017|isbn=978-3-940878-29-8|location=Berlin|page=18|oclc=1042949000|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924224826/https://www.amadeu-antonio-stiftung.de/w/files/englisch/monitoring-2017-englisch-int.pdf|archive-date=2018-09-24|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last1=Korte|first1=Barbara|title=Heroism as a Global Phenomenon in Contemporary Culture|last2=Wendt|first2=Simon|last3=Falkenhayner|first3=Nicole|date=2019|page=[https://books.google.com/books?id=fvWODwAAQBAJ&pg=PT176 PT176]|no-pp=y|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-0429557842|quote=This conspiracy theory, which was first articulated by the French philosopher Renaud Camus, has gained a lot of traction in Europe since 2015.}}</ref>，由法国作家[[雷诺·加缪|雷诺·加缪]]提出。该理论认为，通过与“取代派”精英合谋或合作（''pouvoir/élite remplaciste''）<ref name="taguieff71" /><ref name="fourquet29">{{Harvp|Fourquet|2016}}, [https://books.google.com/books?id=L1AoDQAAQBAJ&pg=PT29 PT29] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=L1AoDQAAQBAJ&pg=PT29 |date=20201015134444 }}.</ref>，欧洲的白人人口可以在人口及文化层面取代非白人人口，特别是[[伊斯兰教|穆斯林]]占多数的国家。取代手段则包括大规模移民、人口增加及[[少子化|降低出生率]]<ref name="taguieff71" /><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Verstraet|first=Antoine|year=2017|title=C'est ça que tu veux ? !|journal=Savoirs et Clinique|language=fr|volume=23|issue=2|pages=55|doi=10.3917/sc.023.0055|issn=1634-3298|quote=[transl. from French] This theory states that the indigenous French ('{{lang|fr|Français de souche}}') could soon be demographically replaced by non-European peoples, especially from the Maghreb and sub-Saharan Africa.}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Harvp|Bergmann|2021|pp=37–38|ps=: "The term ‘The Great Replacement’ rose to new prominence when a deeply controversial French philosopher, Renaud Camus, used it for the title of his book published in 2011. Camus mainly focused on France, but he argued that European civilisation and identity was at risk of being subsumed by mass migration, especially from Muslim countries, and because of low birth rates among the native French people. (...) It found support widely in Europe and was, for instance, entangled in the more general White Genocide conspiracy theory, which nationalist far-right activists have upheld on both sides of the Atlantic.}}</ref>。然而，主流学界并不认同这种主张，认为其源自对移民数据的夸大解读，而且以不科学的种族主义世界观为前提<ref name="Jenkins2017" /><ref>{{Cite news |last=Buncombe |first=Andrew |date=2022-05-17 |title=Inside the data that debunks the 'Great Replacement' theory |work=The Independent |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/buffalo-shooting-great-replacement-theory-b2080389.html |accessdate=2022-05-24 |archive-date=2022-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517134129/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/buffalo-shooting-great-replacement-theory-b2080389.html }}</ref>。

实际上，类似的极右观点早在19世纪就有人提出，只不过到了2011年才由加缪在著作《大取代》（''Le Grand Remplacement''）中正式命名并推广。加缪认为，{{tsl|en|Muslims in France|法国穆斯林}}占了人口相当大的比例，可能会威胁甚至摧毁[[法国文化|法国的文化与文明]]。加缪与其他阴谋论者认为这种过程之所以出现，乃是[[法國政府|法國政府]]、[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]或[[联合国|联合国]]内部的全球派或自由派精英（也就是“取代派”）有意推进的政策造成的。他们认为这种政策是“以替代手段进行的种族灭绝”<ref name="taguieff71"/>。

大取代阴谋论在欧洲获得广泛支持，影响力更遍及其他[[西方世界|西方国家]]的反移民及白人民族主义运动。认同该理论的人士认为“移民之所以涌入白人占多数的国家，是因为他们打算让白人人口在他们的土地上成为少数民族，乃至让本土的白人彻底灭绝”<ref name=":5" />，因此它很大程度上与更加广泛的[[白人種族滅絕陰謀論|白人種族滅絕陰謀論]]密切相关{{NoteTag|在美国[[新纳粹主义|新纳粹主义]]活动分子{{tsl|en|David Lane (white supremacist)|大卫·莱恩}}等人的推动下，西方极右运动自20世纪末盛行<ref name=":0" />。}}<ref name=":5" />，不仅是利用[[伊斯兰恐惧症|伊斯兰恐惧症]]推动{{tsl|en|antisemitic canard|反犹太谣言}}传播，进行战略性替换<ref name=":0">{{Cite book |last=Cosentino |first=Gabriele |title=Social Media and the Post-Truth World Order: The Global Dynamics of Disinformation |date=2020 |publisher=Springer |isbn=978-3-030-43005-4 |page=75 |chapter=From Pizzagate to the Great Replacement: The Globalization of Conspiracy Theories |doi=10.1007/978-3-030-43005-4_3 |quote=While the Great Replacement is at its core an Islamophobic belief, Lane's ideology is anti-Semitic. |s2cid=216239634}}</ref><ref name="camuslebourg206-207" />。

外界认为，大取代阴谋论与其简单的包罗万象的口号是其在泛欧世界中具有更广泛吸引力的原因<ref name="camuslebourg206-207">{{harvp|Camus|Lebourg|2017|pp=206–207|ps=: "The success of that umpteenth incarnation of a theme launched immediately after World War II (Camus has personally declared his indebtedness to Enoch Powell) can be explained by the fact that he subtracted anti-Semitism from the argument."}}</ref>{{sfnp|Chatterton Williams|2017}}{{sfnp|Boubeker|Bancel|Blanchard|2015|pp=141–152}}，尽管这一理论根植于许多白人至上主义运动的反犹太情绪，特别是美国<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Ekman |first=Mattias |date=2022-05-06 |title=The great replacement: Strategic mainstreaming of far-right conspiracy claims |url=http://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/13548565221091983 |journal=Convergence: The International Journal of Research into New Media Technologies |language=en |pages=135485652210919 |doi=10.1177/13548565221091983 |issn=1354-8565 |access-date=2022-05-26 |archive-date=2022-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220526082200/https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/13548565221091983 }}</ref>。尽管加缪公开谴责白人民族主义者的暴力行为<ref name="Heim" /><ref>{{Cite web |last=Byman |first=Daniel |date=2022-05-16 |title=The Global Roots of the Buffalo Shooting |url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2022/05/16/buffalo-mass-shooting-white-supremacist-terrorism-great-replacement-theory/ |website=Foreign Policy |quote=In fact, although white supremacists in the United States and elsewhere have long claimed the white race is under attack, the Great Replacement theory itself originated in France with philosopher Renaud Camus (though Camus himself rejects violence). |access-date=2022-05-26 |archive-date=2022-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220519203345/https://foreignpolicy.com/2022/05/16/buffalo-mass-shooting-white-supremacist-terrorism-great-replacement-theory/ }}</ref>，学者还是认为他将非白人移民描绘成白人人口的外部威胁是在无形中呼吁暴力{{sfnp|Boubeker|Bancel|Blanchard|2015|pp=141–152}}<ref name="Finkielfraut20172">{{harvp|Finkielkraut|2017}}, 23m05s.</ref>。而近年的[[匹兹堡犹太教堂枪击案|2018年匹兹堡犹太教堂枪击案]]、[[基督城清真寺槍擊案|2019年新西兰基督城清真寺枪击案]]、[[2019年埃尔帕索枪击案|2019年埃尔帕索枪击案]]及[[2022年水牛城枪击案|2022年水牛城枪击案]]都有大取代的影子。

== 背景 ==
在近十年来公共舆论中反移民的声音甚嚣尘上的大背景下，法国作家[[雷诺·加缪|雷诺·加缪]]于2010年和2011年发布两部著作，提出了大取代的阴谋论<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Croucher|first=Stephen M.|year=2013|title=Integrated Threat Theory and Acceptance of Immigrant Assimilation: An Analysis of Muslim Immigration in Western Europe|journal=Communication Monographs|volume=80|issue=1|pages=46–62|doi=10.1080/03637751.2012.739704|s2cid=145389928|issn=0363-7751|quote=Such political rhetoric has been effective in the past decade, as more and more individuals in the US and Europe are less accepting of Muslims, particularly Muslim immigrants (Abbas, 2007; Croucher, 2008; Gonzalez et al., 2008).}}</ref>。在2000年代到2010年代的20年间<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.europol.europa.eu/activities-services/main-reports/eu-terrorism-situation-and-trend-report|title=EU Terrorism Situation & Trend Report (Te-Sat)|website=Europol|access-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717165603/https://www.europol.europa.eu/activities-services/main-reports/eu-terrorism-situation-and-trend-report|archive-date=2019-07-17|url-status=live}}</ref>，{{tsl|en|Islamic terrorism in Europe|欧洲伊斯兰恐怖活动|欧洲的伊斯兰恐怖活动}}有上升趋势，再加上2015年兴起的[[欧洲移民危机|欧洲移民危机]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34131911|title=EU migration: Crisis in seven charts|date=2016-03-04|publisher=BBC|access-date=2019-08-06|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131030536/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34131911|archive-date=2016-01-31|language=en-GB}}</ref>，种族间关系愈发紧张，舆论开始接受加缪的理论{{sfnp|Bergmann|2018|pages=126–27}}<ref name="fourquet29"/>。其中移民危机据说证明了人口取代可以在一到两个世代的短时间内发生，尤其有利于加缪思想的传播。与此同时，恐怖活动让认同大取代世界观的人们愈发相信移民是外来威胁<ref name="fourquet29"/>。

另一方面，加缪提出欧洲文化与文明会在未来灭亡的主题也契合当时欧洲知识分子“{{tsl|en|Cultural pessimism|文化悲观}}”与[[對伊斯蘭教的批評|反伊斯兰]]的趋势，在2010年代的多部书名直截了当的畅销著作中有所提及，包括[[蒂洛·薩拉辛|蒂洛·薩拉辛]]的《[[德國正在自取滅亡|德國正在自取滅亡]]》（2010）、[[埃里克·澤穆爾|埃里克·澤穆爾]]的《[[The_French_Suicide|法国的自杀]]》（2014）、[[米歇尔·韦勒贝克|米歇尔·韦勒贝克]]的《[[臣服|臣服]]》（2015）{{sfnp|Polakow-Suransky|2017|pp=2–3}}。

== 雷诺·加缪的概念 ==
[[File:_Autoportrait_de_Renaud_Camus_(mars_2019)_crop.jpg|thumb]]
大取代最早由法国作家[[雷诺·加缪|雷诺·加缪]]在2010年的著作《天真入门手册》（''L'Abécédaire de l'in-nocence''）{{NoteTag|“In-nocence”源于古语“nocence”'<ref>Kennelly, Brian Gordon (2004). "[https://www.academia.edu/2750142/Au_del%C3%A0_de_leurs_dol%C3%A9ances_Au_nom_de_l_In_nocence_Renaud_Camus_and_the_Political Au-delà de leurs doléances, Au nom de l’In-nocence: Renaud Camus and the Political] {{Wayback|url=https://www.academia.edu/2750142/Au_del%C3%A0_de_leurs_dol%C3%A9ances_Au_nom_de_l_In_nocence_Renaud_Camus_and_the_Political |date=20220526082201 }}", ''California Polytechnic State University''.</ref>，意为“伤害、滋扰、恶意、内疚”，是法语和英语单词“innocence”的词源<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://micmap.org/dicfro/search/dictionnaire-godefroy/nocence|title=D. Godefroy|access-date=2022-05-24|archive-date=2021-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104220718/http://micmap.org/dicfro/search/dictionnaire-godefroy/nocence}}</ref>。}}<ref name="camusmathieu">{{Cite web|last1=Camus|first1=Jean-Yves|last2=Mathieu|first2=Annie|date=2017-08-19|title=D'où vient l'expression 'remigration'?|url=https://www.lesoleil.com/actualite/dou-vient-lexpression-remigration-093e01598c270a4ca9a94070d4bb5980|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524102419/https://www.lesoleil.com/actualite/dou-vient-lexpression-remigration-093e01598c270a4ca9a94070d4bb5980|archive-date=2019-05-24|website=Le Soleil}}</ref>及次年的同名著作《大取代》（{{lang-en|The Great Replacement (introduction to global replacism}}）中提及。加缪表示“大取代”这个词是自己偶然间想到的，可能或多或少无意间参考了18世纪[[阿卡迪亚人|阿卡迪亚人]]的{{tsl|en|Expulsion of the Acadians|驱逐阿卡迪亚人|大骚乱}}（''Grand Dérangement''）<ref name="finkielkraut4m25s">{{Harvp|Finkielkraut|2017}}，4分25秒.</ref>。他表示，德国诗人[[贝托尔特·布莱希特|贝托尔特·布莱希特]]曾讽刺地认为政府最容易做的事情就是在人民丧失信心的情况下改变他们（“难道政府不可以把人民解散掉，然后再选一个吗？”），而大取代理论就是这个主张的“生动写照”<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Leconte|first=Cécile|year=2019|title=La carrière militante du " grand remplacement " au sein du milieu partisan de l'Alternative pour l'Allemagne (AfD)|journal=Politix|volume=126|issue=2|pages=111–134|doi=10.3917/pox.126.0111|s2cid=210566278}}</ref>。

加缪认为，大取代理论受“[[工业化|工业化]]”、“[[世俗化|世俗化]]”和“去文化化”{{NoteTag|{{lang|fr|déculturation}}，可以翻译为个人文化或民族情感的“损失”、“消失”、“佚失”<ref>{{Cite book|title=Vue d'oeil: Journal 2012|last=Camus|first=Renaud|date=2013|page=[https://books.google.com/books?id=fgH7c4mw6m4C&pg=PT21 PT21]|no-pp=y|publisher=Fayard|isbn=978-2213672892|language=fr}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Traverso|first=Enzo|title=The New Faces of Fascism: Populism and the Far Right|date=2019|publisher=Verso Books|isbn=978-1788730495|pages=71}}</ref>。}}滋养。在他看来，当今的[[唯物主义|唯物主义]]社会与[[全球主義|全球主義]]思想已经创造出一批“可以被取代的人类，不论国家、民族、文化为何”<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.lemonde.fr/politique/article/2014/01/23/le-grand-boniment_4353499_823448.html|title=Le fantasme du 'grand remplacement' démographique|last=Joignot|first=Frédéric|date=2014-01-23|work=Le Monde|access-date=2019-08-04|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521014256/https://www.lemonde.fr/politique/article/2014/01/23/le-grand-boniment_4353499_823448.html|archive-date=2019-05-21|language=fr}}</ref>，也就是他所认为的“全球取代”<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Bromley|first=Roger|year=2018|title=The politics of displacement: the Far Right narrative of Europe and its 'others'|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/328539266|journal=From the European South. University of Nottingham|volume=3|pages=15|access-date=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010233316/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/328539266}}</ref>。不过，他觉得“大取代不需要定义”，而且词的本身不是“概念”，而是“现象”<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.liberation.fr/france/2015/10/13/le-grand-remplacement-totem-extreme_1403361|title=Le 'grand remplacement', totem extrême|last=Albertini|first=Dominique|date=2015-10-13|website=Libération|language=fr|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701032837/https://www.liberation.fr/france/2015/10/13/le-grand-remplacement-totem-extreme_1403361|archive-date=2019-07-01|access-date=2019-08-03}}</ref>{{sfnp|Chatterton Williams|2017}}。

根据加缪的理论，土生法国人是“被取代者”（''les remplacés''）<ref name="finkielkraut4m25s"/>，在人口层面已经被主要来自非洲或中东的外来人口取代，正处在“取代派力量”鼓励的“人口移民”进程中<ref name="taguieff71"/><ref name="oxfordresearch">{{cite web|url=https://www.oxfordresearchgroup.org.uk/blog/fear-filled-apocalypses-the-far-rights-use-of-conspiracy-theory|title=Fear-Filled Apocalypses: The Far-Right's Use of Conspiracy Theories|last1=Wilson|first1=Andrew|date=2019-03-27|website=Oxford Research Group|access-date=2019-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404164059/https://www.oxfordresearchgroup.org.uk/blog/fear-filled-apocalypses-the-far-rights-use-of-conspiracy-theory|archive-date=2019-04-04|url-status=live}}</ref>。他以1940年到1945年[[第二次世界大战德占法国军事管辖区|德国纳粹占领的法国地区]]为例，当时的“殖民者”/“占领者”（''colonisateurs/colonisation''）没有欧洲人血统但住在欧洲<ref name="Heim"/><ref name="figaro-04-19"/>，将他眼中的“取代派精英”斥为“同流合污者”<ref name="Finkielfraut2017"/>。2017年，加缪创办{{tsl|en|National Council of European Resistance|欧洲抵抗运动全国委员会}}组织，在名称上借鉴了[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间的[[全國抵抗委員會|全國抵抗委員會]]（1943–1945）<ref name="sapiro377">{{Cite book|last=Sapiro|first=Gisèle|title=Les écrivains et la politique en France – De l'affaire Dreyfus à la guerre d'Algérie|date=2018|page=[https://books.google.com/books?id=BWluDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT377 PT377]|no-pp=y|publisher=Le Seuil|isbn=978-2-02-140215-5|language=fr}}</ref>，以法国[[法國抵抗運動|抵抗纳粹党]]为例子暗示大家仇恨他眼中的“占领者”（也就是移民人士），甚至采用暴力等直接行动<ref name="Finkielfraut2017">{{harvp|Finkielkraut|2017}}, 23m05s.</ref>。他认为大取代和所谓的“[[白人種族滅絕陰謀論|以替换方式灭绝欧洲人]]”如同[[纳粹大屠杀|纳粹大屠杀]]<ref name="sapiro377"/>。

=== 据称造成的影响 ===
{{See also|{{le|圣人营|The Camp of the Saints}}|血河演說}}
在2011年著作《大取代》的尾声中，加缪提到了两个影响深远的人物，一个是英国政治家[[以諾·鮑威爾|以諾·鮑威爾]]，一个是法国作家{{tsl|en|Jean Raspail|让·拉斯佩尔}}。鲍威尔曾在1968年的[[血河演說|血河演說]]认为未来的种族关系会造成世界末日，拉斯佩尔在1973年的小说《{{le|圣人营|The Camp of the Saints}}》认为[[第三世界|第三世界]]的移民大潮会让西方世界轰然崩塌<ref name="camuslebourg206-207"/>{{sfnp|Polakow-Suransky|2017|p=210}}。

在2016年《[[旁观者|旁观者]]》杂志的一篇文章，加缪表示理解大取代理论的钥匙就在他2002年的著作《感觉》（''Du Sens''）中<ref name="Spectator">{{cite news|url=https://life.spectator.co.uk/2016/11/non/|title=Non!|last1=Sexton|first1=David|date=2016-11-03|work=The Spectator|access-date=2018-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180821031918/https://life.spectator.co.uk/2016/11/non/|archive-date=2018-08-21|url-status=live}}</ref>。在《感觉》一书中，加缪认为“法兰西”和“法国”两个词在自然及物理现实层面相同，在法律层面不相同，类似于[[夏尔·莫拉斯|夏尔·莫拉斯]]对“合法国家”（''pays légal''）及“现实国家”（''pays réel''）的{{tsl|en|cratylism|克拉蒂卢斯主义|克拉蒂卢斯式}}区分<ref name="Chaouat">{{cite news|url=https://www.tabletmag.com/jewish-news-and-politics/europe/290272/renaud-camus-great-replacement|title=The gay French poet behind the alt-right's favorite catch phrase|last1=Chaouat|first1=Bruno|date=2019-08-27|work=Tablet Magazine|access-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828200722/https://www.tabletmag.com/jewish-news-and-politics/europe/290272/renaud-camus-great-replacement|archive-date=2019-08-28|url-status=live}}</ref>。在同一个采访中，加缪表示自己对大取代阴谋论的想象可以追溯到1996年，当时他正修订法国南部省份[[埃罗省|埃罗省]]的指南：“我突然间意识到在一些历史悠久的村庄里，人口也彻底改变了。我就是在那个时候开始写相关的内容<ref name="Spectator"/>。”

== 类似概念 ==
{{Main|白人種族滅絕陰謀論}}
尽管有自己的奇点和概念，大取代理论还是属于范围更广、历史更久远的[[白人種族滅絕陰謀論|白人種族滅絕陰謀論]]{{Sfnp|Bergmann|2018|pp=127–128}}。白人种族灭绝论于1995年由美国新纳粹主义者{{tsl|en|David Lane (white supremacist)|大卫·莱恩}}在1995年著作《白人种族灭绝宣言》（''White Genocide Manifesto''）中提出，当中莱恩断言[[西方世界|西方世界]]国家的政府打算将白人变成“灭绝物种”<ref name="TDCWN2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2016/09/how-the-turner-diaries-changed-white-nationalism/500039/|title=How 'The Turner Diaries' Changed White Nationalism|last=Berger|first=J. M.|work=The Atlantic|access-date=2017-11-24|language=en-US|quote=The manifesto itself was soon reduced to the simple phrase 'white genocide', which proliferated at the start of the 21st century and has become the overwhelmingly dominant meme of modern white nationalism.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806175641/https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2016/09/how-the-turner-diaries-changed-white-nationalism/500039/|archive-date=2019-08-06|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2016/12/26/drexel_censures_professor_for_white_genocide_tweet.html|title=Drexel University, Apparently Unfamiliar With White Supremacist Lingo, Censures Prof For 'White Genocide' Tweet|last=Dessem|first=Matthew|date=2016-12-26|work=Slate|access-date=2017-11-24|language=en-US|issn=1091-2339|quote=Although it's difficult to date precisely, white supremacist publishing houses being somewhat less reliable than [[西蒙與舒斯特|Simon & Schuster]], that honor probably belongs to the late David Lane, terrorist, white supremacist, and author of an execrable little essay called 'White Genocide Manifesto'.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181015051648/http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2016/12/26/drexel_censures_professor_for_white_genocide_tweet.html|archive-date=2018-10-15|url-status=live}}</ref>。实际上，在敌对势力精英的指引下“取代”土生白人的思想最早可以追溯到二战前的{{tsl|en|Antisemitic canards|反犹谣言}}。该谣言假设犹太人密谋通过通婚摧毁欧洲，在{{tsl|en|Édouard Drumont|爱德华·德鲁蒙}}的[[反犹太主义|反犹太主义]]畅销书《{{tsl|en|La France juive|犹太法国}}》中尤为突出{{sfnp|Weil|Truong|2015}}。在提到两者的相似性时，历史学家{{tsl|en|Nicolas Lebourg|尼古拉斯·勒伯格}}和政治学家{{tsl|en|Jean-Yves Camus|让-伊夫·加缪}}认为雷诺·加缪的贡献是用穆斯林和欧洲人之间的文明冲突来取代原来的反犹元素<ref name="camuslebourg206-207"/>。

撰写民族主义立场专栏文章的[[莫里斯·巴雷斯|莫里斯·巴雷斯]]认为“大取代”的意识形态系谱与当时的时代背景息息相关。他认为，1889年和1900年这两年的法国土生人口在移民及生育率下降的联合作用下被取代<ref>{{Cite book|title=Le Nouveau FN. Les vieux habits du populisme: Les vieux habits du populisme|last=Kauffmann|first=Grégoire|date=2016|page=[https://books.google.com/books?id=IY_gDAAAQBAJ&pg=PT78 PT78]|no-pp=y|publisher=Le Seuil|isbn=978-2021300307|language=fr}}</ref>{{sfnp|Weil|Truong|2015}}。另外，学界认为战后欧洲的新法西斯主义与新纳粹主义思想家也有类似的看法，其中又以{{tsl|en|Maurice Bardèche|莫里斯·巴尔代什}}、{{tsl|en|René Binet (neo-Fascist)|雷内·比奈}}和{{tsl|en|Gaston-Armand Amaudruz|加斯顿-阿曼德·阿莫德鲁兹}}最为突出<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.lemonde.fr/idees/article/2018/09/06/une-partie-de-l-extreme-droite-europeenne-revient-a-l-action-violente_5350854_3232.html|title=En Europe, une partie de l'extrême droite revient à l'action violente|last=François|first=Stéphane|date=2018-09-06|work=Le Monde|access-date=2019-08-03|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822234807/https://www.lemonde.fr/idees/article/2018/09/06/une-partie-de-l-extreme-droite-europeenne-revient-a-l-action-violente_5350854_3232.html|archive-date=2019-08-22|language=fr}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.lemonde.fr/blog/antiracisme/2014/11/03/le-grand-remplacement-et-le-polypier-geant/|title=Le Grand Remplacement et le polypier géant|last=Debono|first=Emmanuel|date=2014-11-03|work=Le Monde|access-date=2019-08-16|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816212016/https://www.lemonde.fr/blog/antiracisme/2014/11/03/le-grand-remplacement-et-le-polypier-geant/|archive-date=2019-08-16|language=fr}}</ref>。

而大取代思想的最近期来源理论是由2005年英国作家{{tsl|en|Bat Ye'or|巴特·耶奥}}提出的“[[欧拉伯|欧拉伯]]”，加缪经常称这个理论是大取代思想的灵感来源<ref name="Abdeslam">{{cite journal|last1=Ait Abdeslam|first1=Abderrahim|year=2018|title=The vilification of Muslim diaspora in French fictional novels: 'Soumission' (2015) and 'Petit Frère' (2008) as case studies|journal=Journal of Multicultural Discourses|volume=13|issue=3|pages=232–242|doi=10.1080/17447143.2018.1511717|s2cid=216116710}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.monde-diplomatique.fr/2014/05/LIOGIER/50422|title=Le mythe de l'invasion arabo-musulmane|last=Liogier|first=Raphaël|date=2014-05-01|website=Le Monde diplomatique|language=fr|access-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806122217/https://www.monde-diplomatique.fr/2014/05/LIOGIER/50422|archive-date=2019-08-06|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nouvelobs.com/le-dossier-de-l-obs/20120921.OBS3170/reacosphere-le-conspirationnisme-est-au-coeur-de-la-dynamique.html#modal-msg|title=Réacosphère : "Le conspirationnisme est au coeur de la dynamique"|last1=Gross|first1=Estelle|work=L'Obs|access-date=2019-08-06|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822160528/https://www.nouvelobs.com/le-dossier-de-l-obs/20120921.OBS3170/reacosphere-le-conspirationnisme-est-au-coeur-de-la-dynamique.html#modal-msg|archive-date=2019-08-22|last2=Cahuzac|first2=Yannick|language=fr}}</ref>。这个理论同样涉及到法国与阿拉伯国家联合推动的[[全球主义|全球主义]]组织，认为两者希望以此推动欧洲伊斯兰化，让穆斯林通过移民及高生育率淹没欧洲大陆<ref name="MarjanSapir">{{cite book|title=Europe's Destiny|last=Marján|first=Attila|author2=André Sapir|publisher=Johns Hopkins University Press|year=2010|isbn=978-0-8018-9547-0|location=Baltimore, MD|page=161}}</ref>。该理论还将移民者形容为入侵者、[[第五纵队|第五纵队]]，是腐败的政治精英请过来的<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thespinoff.co.nz/media/28-03-2019/how-the-swarm-of-white-extremism-spreads-itself-online/|title=How the swarm of white extremism spreads itself online|last=Ganesh|first=Bharath|date=2019-03-28|publisher=The Spinoff|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423004445/https://thespinoff.co.nz/media/28-03-2019/how-the-swarm-of-white-extremism-spreads-itself-online/|archive-date=2019-04-23|access-date=2019-08-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2014/apr/03/muslims-are-coming-islamophobia-extremism-domestic-war-on-terror-review|title=The Muslims Are Coming!: Islamophobia, Extremism, and the Domestic War on Terror – review|author=Robin Yassin-Kassab|date=2014-04-03|work=The Guardian|access-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424133053/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2014/apr/03/muslims-are-coming-islamophobia-extremism-domestic-war-on-terror-review|archive-date=2019-04-24|url-status=live}}</ref>。学界普遍认为，加缪尽管没有提出相关的主题，但确实创造了“大取代”这个口号和概念，推动其在2010年代声名鹊起<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.lemonde.fr/politique/article/2019/03/15/attaque-en-nouvelle-zelande-le-plus-important-pour-la-lutte-raciale-selon-le-suspect-c-est-internet_5436816_823448.html|title=Attentat en Nouvelle-Zélande : L'auteur de l'attaque se reconnaît comme fasciste|last1=Soullier|first1=Lucie|date=2019-03-15|work=Le Monde|access-date=2019-08-06|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806190359/https://www.lemonde.fr/politique/article/2019/03/15/attaque-en-nouvelle-zelande-le-plus-important-pour-la-lutte-raciale-selon-le-suspect-c-est-internet_5436816_823448.html|archive-date=2019-08-06|last2=Lebourg|first2=Nicolas|language=fr}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lci.fr/population/attentat-de-christchurch-et-grand-remplacement-itineraire-d-une-theorie-proteiforme-2115835.html|title=Attentat de Christchurch et 'grand remplacement' : itinéraire d'une théorie protéiforme|last=Condomines|first=Anaïs|website=LCI|date=2019-03-19 |language=fr|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723181254/https://www.lci.fr/population/attentat-de-christchurch-et-grand-remplacement-itineraire-d-une-theorie-proteiforme-2115835.html|archive-date=2019-07-23|access-date=2019-08-06|quote=Valérie Igounet: 'certaines personnes ont cité cette théorie avant Camus mais c'est bien lui qui l'a popularisée. L'association de ces deux mots a fait mouche dans un contexte français particulier, et ce de manière très récente'}}</ref>。

== 分析 ==
=== 人口统计 ===
尽管法国各民族的人口在[[法國人口|战后移民]]的推动下出现转变，学界还是对大取代的主张不以为然，认为这只是过度解读移民数据与非科学的种族偏见观点造成的结果<ref name="Jenkins2017">{{cite book|last=Jenkins|first=Cecil|title=A Brief History of France|date=2017|publisher=Little, Brown Book Group|isbn=978-1-4721-4027-2|page=[https://books.google.com/books?id=UjreDQAAQBAJ&pg=PT342 PT342]|no-pp=y|quote=As for the ''grand replacement'', this has been widely seen as a paranoid fantasy, which plays fast and loose with the statistics, is racist in that it classes as immigrants people actually born in France, glosses over the fact that around half of immigrants are from other European countries, and suggests that declining indigenous France will be outbred by Muslim newcomers when in fact it has the highest fertility rate in Western Europe, and ''not'' because of immigration.}}</ref>。地理学家兰迪斯·麦凯勒（Landis MacKellar）批评加缪假设“第三代和第四代移民不知什么原因不是法国人”<ref name="MacKellar_2016">{{cite journal |last1=MacKellar |first1=Landis |year=2016 |title=Review: La République islamique de France? A Review Essay |journal=Population and Development Review |volume=42 |issue=2 |pages=368–375 |doi=10.1111/j.1728-4457.2016.00130.x |jstor=44015644 |quote=Michèle Tribalat of the Institut National d'Études Démographiques (INED) has argued that the restriction forces policymakers to proceed with eyes wide shut, but Hervé Le Bras of the École d'Hautes Études en Sciences Sociales (EHESS) counters that such statistics simply objectify and dignify racist prejudices. Both views have some validity. Whichever way you feel, a consequence of our ignorance is that the specter of Le Grand Remplacement haunts French politics |hdl-access=free |hdl=10.1111/padr.2016.42.issue-2}}</ref>。根据不同专家的估计，2017年法国穆斯林人口占总体8.8%到12.5%<ref name=":1">{{cite web|date=2017-11-29|title=Europe's Growing Muslim Population|url=https://www.pewforum.org/2017/11/29/europes-growing-muslim-population/|access-date=2020-12-13|website=Pew Research Center|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211171251/https://www.pewforum.org/2017/11/29/europes-growing-muslim-population/}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Héran|first=François|title=Avec l'immigration: Mesurer, débattre, agir|publisher=La Découverte|year=2017|isbn=978-2707195821|page=20}}</ref>，在麦凯勒眼中远远不及“取代”的程度<ref name="MacKellar_2016" />。[[皮尤研究中心|皮尤研究中心]]预测在没有移民的情况下，法国的平均生育率到2050年会增加到12.7%，计算移民情况在内，生育率增加到18%<ref name=":1" />。另据[[法国国家统计与经济研究所|法国国家统计与经济研究所]]数据，2018年[[法国本土|法国本土]]的新生儿中，28.15%的父母至少一方不在欧洲出生<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insee.fr/fr/statistiques/fichier/4647540/T37quater.xlsx|title=T37QUATER – Nés vivants selon le pays de naissance des parents|website=Insee.fr|access-date=2022-05-24|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112194654/https://www.insee.fr/fr/statistiques/fichier/4647540/T37quater.xlsx}}</ref>。[[美国普查局|美国普查局]]预测美国白人人口到2044年会下降至不到一半；尽管种族区分、跨种族通婚及移民会让这个日期进一步推迟，支持大取代理论的人士还是对这个现象感到焦虑<ref>{{Cite news|last=Tavernise|first=Sabrina|date=2018-11-22|title=Why the Announcement of a Looming White Minority Makes Demographers Nervous|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/11/22/us/white-americans-minority-population.html|access-date=2021-10-13|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029225634/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/11/22/us/white-americans-minority-population.html}}</ref>。

=== 种族内涵 ===
澳大利亚历史学家{{tsl|en|A. Dirk Moses|A·德克·摩西}}认为大取代理念某种程度上是欧洲人的心理[[投射|投射]]。欧洲人一方面制定{{tsl|en|settler colonialism|定居殖民主义|定居殖民}}计划，通过{{tsl|en|settler societies|定居者社会}}消除和替换本地人口，另一方面害怕这种政策会反过来影响自己<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Moses |first1=A. Dirk |title=“White Genocide” and the Ethics of Public Analysis |journal=Journal of Genocide Research |date=2019 |volume=21 |issue=2 |pages=201–213 |doi=10.1080/14623528.2019.1599493|quote=In its fixation on demographic substitution, the fear [in Great Replacement theory] mimics settler colonial theory, which highlights how this form of colonialism is marked not primarily exploitation of native labour but through its elimination and replacement by immigrant-settlers: one society displaces another. Camus – and Tarrant who likely takes the French site of his “enlightenment” story from him – fear they are native victims of reverse settler colonialism. Not for nothing does he talk about the “colonization of Europe today.”}}</ref>。

在德语语境中，奥地利政治学家{{tsl|en|Rainer Bauböck|雷纳·鲍博克}}质疑阴谋论者对“人口替换”或“更换”（''Bevölkerungsaustausch''）二词的使用。根据{{tsl|en|Ruth Wodak|露丝·沃达克}}认为需要在历史背景中看待大取代口号的分析，鲍博克认为大取代理论是纳粹{{tsl|en|Umvolkung|种族倒置}}的重现<ref>{{cite news|url=https://derstandard.at/2000102690976/Bevoelkerungsaustausch-oder-Umvolkung-Erklaeren-Sie-den-Unterschied-Herr-Vizekanzler|title=Bevölkerungsaustausch oder Umvolkung? Erklären Sie den Unterschied, Herr Strache!|author=Bauböck, Rainer|date=2019-05-07|newspaper=Der Standard|language=de|trans-title=Population exchange or change? Explain the difference, Mr. Strache!|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520073346/https://derstandard.at/2000102690976/Bevoelkerungsaustausch-oder-Umvolkung-Erklaeren-Sie-den-Unterschied-Herr-Vizekanzler|archive-date=2019-05-20|url-status=live}}</ref>。

=== 流传 ===
[[File:Tract_du_NON_pour_Jour_de_colère.jpg|thumb]]
学界认为，大取代之所以流传甚广，是因为有两个决定性因素，一是由加缪主张衍生的万金油口号——“你们（现在）只有一个种族，但是在一代人的时间内，你们会有不同的种族”，二是加缪去除了最初新纳粹主义者[[白人種族滅絕陰謀論|白人種族滅絕陰謀論]]中的反犹太元素{{sfnp|Boubeker|Bancel|Blanchard|2015|pp=141–152}}<ref name="camuslebourg206-207"/>。[[反诽谤联盟|反诽谤联盟]]表示，由于许多白人至上主义者（尤其是美国的）将非白人移民归咎于犹太人，大取代如今（指2021年）添上了反犹太色彩<ref name=":4">{{Cite web |title=“The Great Replacement:” An Explainer |url=https://www.adl.org/resources/backgrounders/the-great-replacement-an-explainer |access-date=2022-05-25 |website=Anti-Defamation League |language=en |archive-date=2022-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220521203418/https://www.adl.org/resources/backgrounders/the-great-replacement-an-explainer }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Jones |first=Dustin |date=2022-05-16 |title=What is the 'great replacement' and how is it tied to the Buffalo shooting suspect? |language=en |work=NPR |url=https://www.npr.org/2022/05/16/1099034094/what-is-the-great-replacement-theory |access-date=2022-05-25 |archive-date=2022-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517073243/https://www.npr.org/2022/05/16/1099034094/what-is-the-great-replacement-theory }}</ref>。学者{{le|凯瑟琳·贝卢|Kathleen Belew}}认为大取代让“机会主义者得以选择敌人”，但也遵循中心的激励逻辑，即保护内部的东西（保障白人的出生率），不管外面的敌人<ref>{{Cite web |last=Chotiner |first=Isaac |date=2022-05-15 |title=Making Sense of the Racist Mass Shooting in Buffalo |url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/q-and-a/making-sense-of-the-racist-mass-shooting-in-buffalo |access-date=2022-05-25 |website=The New Yorker |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220523131310/https://www.newyorker.com/news/q-and-a/making-sense-of-the-racist-mass-shooting-in-buffalo }}</ref>。

2018年12月，{{tsl|en|Institut français d'opinion publique|法国民意研究所}}的一项调查显示25%的国民认同大取代理论，46%认为自己是“[[黄背心运动|黄背心运动]]”的抗议者<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lejdd.fr/Societe/sondage-les-gilets-jaunes-sont-plus-sensibles-aux-theories-du-complot-3855563|title=Sondage : les Gilets jaunes sont plus sensibles aux théories du complot|last=Liabot|first=Thomas|website=Le Journal du Dimanche|language=fr|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427121621/https://www.lejdd.fr/Societe/sondage-les-gilets-jaunes-sont-plus-sensibles-aux-theories-du-complot-3855563|archive-date=2019-04-27|access-date=2019-08-03}}</ref>。到了2021年10月，{{tsl|en|The Harris Poll|哈里斯民意研究院}}的调查显示61%的国民相信法国会出现大取代，67%担心大取代出现<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-10-21|title=67% de Français inquiets par l'idée d'un "grand remplacement", selon un sondage|url=https://www.lefigaro.fr/actualite-france/67-de-francais-inquiets-par-l-idee-d-un-grand-remplacement-selon-un-sondage-20211021|url-status=live|website=Le Figaro|access-date=2022-05-24|archive-date=2022-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220428052323/https://www.lefigaro.fr/actualite-france/67-de-francais-inquiets-par-l-idee-d-un-grand-remplacement-selon-un-sondage-20211021}}</ref>。

与此同时，大取代理论也深刻印象了其他国家的极右翼及白人民族主义群体<ref name="Wildman">{{cite news |url=https://www.vox.com/world/2017/8/15/16141456/renaud-camus-the-great-replacement-you-will-not-replace-us-charlottesville-white |title='You will not replace us': a French philosopher explains the Charlottesville chant |last=Wildman |first=Sarah |date=2017-08-15 |work=Vox |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180809053929/https://www.vox.com/world/2017/8/15/16141456/renaud-camus-the-great-replacement-you-will-not-replace-us-charlottesville-white |archive-date=2018-08-09 |url-status=live }}</ref>。加拿大极右翼政治运动家{{tsl|en|Lauren Southern|劳伦·索顿}}在2017年7月发布的视频中介绍了大取代理念，到2020年吸引68.6万次观看<ref>{{Cite AV media|title=The Great Replacement|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OTDmsmN43NA|access-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200430173227/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OTDmsmN43NA|archive-date=2020-04-30|url-status=live}}</ref>，被认为是普及大取代理论的重要推手<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/the-great-replacement-the-racist-idea-now-at-the-heart-of-europe-s-politics-20190319-p515cc.html|title='The Great Replacement': an idea now at the heart of Europe's politics|last1=Miller|first1=Nick|date=2019-03-19|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|access-date=2019-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331235005/https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/the-great-replacement-the-racist-idea-now-at-the-heart-of-europe-s-politics-20190319-p515cc.html|archive-date=2019-03-31|url-status=live}}</ref>。挪威{{tsl|en|Counter-jihad|反圣战}}博主{{tsl|en|Fjordman|Fjordman}}也传播了大取代理论<ref name="lemonde2019">{{cite news|url=https://mondediplo.com/outsidein/white-supremacists-mainstream|title='White genocide' theorists worm their way into the West's mainstream|last1=Ahmed|first1=Nafeez|date=2019-03-25|work=Le Monde diplomatique|access-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407144453/https://mondediplo.com/outsidein/white-supremacists-mainstream|archive-date=2019-04-07|url-status=live}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Gates of Vienna|维也纳之门}}、{{tsl|en|Politically Incorrect (blog)|政治不正确}}、Fdesouche等知名极右翼平台为博主传播推广大取代理论搭建了平台<ref name="Betz">{{cite book|title=The Oxford Handbook of the Radical Right|last=Betz|first=Hans-Georg|year=2018|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0190644185|editor-last=Rydgren|editor-first=Jens|volume=1|chapter=5. The Radical Right and Populism|doi=10.1093/oxfordhb/9780190274559.013.5|lccn=2017025436|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=--5IDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT121|access-date=2022-05-24|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416015612/https://books.google.com/books?id=--5IDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT121}}</ref>，而理论的主要推广者也结成了一个或多或少与白人民族主义运动有联系的大型网络（尤其是欧洲的{{tsl|en|Identitarian movement|同一性运动}}<ref>{{cite web |last1=Dearden|first1=Lizzie |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/generation-identity-far-right-group-training-camps-europe-uk-recruits-military-white-nationalist-a8046641.html |title=Generation Identity: Far-right group sending UK recruits to military-style training camps in Europe |date=2017-11-09 |work=The Independent |quote=...claims it represents "indigenous Europeans" and propagates the far-right conspiracy theory that white people are becoming a minority in what it calls the "Great Replacement" |access-date=2018-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925222918/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/generation-identity-far-right-group-training-camps-europe-uk-recruits-military-white-nationalist-a8046641.html |archive-date=2018-09-25 |url-status=live  }}</ref>、德国的[[愛國歐洲人反對西方伊斯蘭化|愛國歐洲人反對西方伊斯蘭化]]等<ref name="Deutsche Welle">{{cite news|url=https://www.dw.com/en/how-dangerous-are-austrias-far-right-hipsters/a-45241401|title=How dangerous are Austria's far-right hipsters?|last1=Meaker|first1=Morgan|date=2018-08-28|access-date=2018-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924185820/https://www.dw.com/en/how-dangerous-are-austrias-far-right-hipsters/a-45241401|archive-date=2018-09-24|url-status=live|publisher=Deutsche Welle|location=Vienna|quote=...and spread the 'great replacement' conspiracy theory—the idea that white Europeans will be replaced by people from the Middle East and Africa through immigration. The theory is based on inflated statistics and un-substantiated demographic projections. Right now, only 4 percent of the European Union is made up of non-EU nationals.}}</ref>）。

2022年5月，[[美联社|美联社]]称三分之一的美国成年人认为有迹象显示“本土美国人正被以选举目的取代移民”。民调显示，从保守派及极右派媒体接受新闻资讯的人更倾向于相信大取代理论，其中[[同一个美国新闻网|同一个美国新闻网]]和[[大全新闻|大全新闻]]的观众有45%相信大取代，福斯新闻有31%的观众相信，相比之下[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]只有13%的人相信，[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]只有11%<ref>{{Cite web |title=Immigration Attitudes and Conspiratorial Thinkers: A Study Issued on the 10th Anniversary of The Associated Press-NORC Center for Public Affairs Research |url=https://apnorc.org/projects/immigration-attitudes-and-conspiratorial-thinkers/ |access-date=2022-05-16 |website=AP-NORC |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513005716/https://apnorc.org/projects/immigration-attitudes-and-conspiratorial-thinkers/ }}</ref>。

==政治影响==
===欧洲===
====法国====
在法国舆论及媒体的推波助澜下，大取代阴谋论在大多数欧洲人中传播。法国的右翼民族主义团体断言[[法兰西人|土生法兰西人]]正进行“伊斯兰替换”，认为{{tsl|en|Islam in France|法国穆斯林人口}}是潜在威胁，可能会对[[法国文化|法国文化与文明]]构成破坏<ref name="Le Pen advisor">{{cite web |last1=Osborne|first1=Samuel |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/marine-le-pen-adviser-robert-menard-guilty-muslim-islam-hatred-latest-a7701721.html |title=Marine Le Pen adviser found guilty of inciting hatred against Muslims |date=2017-04-25 |work=The Independent |access-date=2018-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924002118/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/marine-le-pen-adviser-robert-menard-guilty-muslim-islam-hatred-latest-a7701721.html |archive-date=2018-09-24 |url-status=live  }}</ref><ref name="Froio">{{cite journal |last1=Froio |first1=Caterina |title=Race, Religion, or Culture? Framing Islam between Racism and Neo-Racism in the Online Network of the French Far Right |journal=Perspectives on Politics |date=2018-08-21 |volume=16 |issue=3 |pages=696–709 |doi=10.1017/S1537592718001573 |s2cid=149865406 |quote=...the conspiracy theory of the Grand remplacement (Great replacement) positing the 'Islamo-substitution' of biologically autochthonous populations in the French metropolitan territory, by Muslim minorities mostly coming from sub-Saharan Africa and the Maghreb}}</ref><ref name="La Croix">{{cite news |last1=Schneider|first1=Frédérique |url=https://www.la-croix.com/France/Exclusion/VIDEO-campagne-deconstruire-discours-complotistes-Internet-2018-01-26-1200909107 |format=Video |title= Une campagne pour déconstruire les discours complotistes sur Internet |date=2018-01-26 |newspaper=La Croix |language=fr |quote=...le " grand remplacement ", une théorie de type conspirationniste selon laquelle il existerait un processus de remplacement des Français sur leur sol par des non-Européens. |access-date=2018-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180923235223/https://www.la-croix.com/France/Exclusion/VIDEO-campagne-deconstruire-discours-complotistes-Internet-2018-01-26-1200909107 |archive-date=2018-09-23 |url-status=live  }}</ref>。

2011年，极右翼政治人物[[玛丽娜·勒庞|玛丽娜·勒庞]]借大取代阴谋论主张法国境内的“反对派”正反动道德战和经济战，通过“有组织地替换我们的人口让它（法国）沉没”<ref name="Identity politics">{{cite web|url=http://theconversation.com/politiques-identitaires-et-mythe-du-grand-remplacement-117471|title=Politiques identitaires et mythe du " grand remplacement "|language=fr|trans-title=Identity politics and the myth of the "great replacement"|publisher=The Conversation|date=2019-06-16|access-date=2019-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711112448/http://theconversation.com/politiques-identitaires-et-mythe-du-grand-remplacement-117471|archive-date=2019-07-11|url-status=live}}</ref>。2013年，历史学家{{tsl|en|Dominique Venner|多米尼克·文纳}}在[[巴黎聖母院|巴黎聖母院]]自杀，以一张概述“取代我们人民的罪行”的字条作为遗言。消息认为，文纳的遗言激励极右翼的伊利亚特学院（Iliade Institute）以大取代理念为意识形态宗旨<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2018/04/17/iliade-institute-french-far-right-intellectuals-rewrite-european-history|title=At the Iliade Institute, French far-right intellectuals rewrite European history|website=The Southern Poverty Law Center|date=2019-04-17|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517224622/https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2018/04/17/iliade-institute-french-far-right-intellectuals-rewrite-european-history|archive-date=2019-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>。提及大取代理念的时候，勒庞公开赞扬文纳最后的举动明显是在政治层面唤醒[[法兰西人|法兰西人]]<ref name="Identity politics"/>。

2015年，新右派作家{{tsl|en|Guillaume Faye|纪尧姆·法耶}}在斯德哥尔摩的[[瑞典军事博物馆|瑞典军事博物馆]]发表谈话，认为所谓的大取代运动通过堕胎、同性恋、移民三大社会议题对付欧洲人，直言穆斯林群体把生育率当成人口武器，以此取代白人人口<ref name="Expo">{{cite web|url=https://expo.se/myten-om-det-stora-utbytet|title=Myten om det stora utbytet|language=sv|trans-title=The myth of the great exchange|work=Expo|date=2019-03-15|access-date=2019-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190710132752/https://expo.se/myten-om-det-stora-utbytet|archive-date=2019-07-10|url-status=live}}</ref>。

2017年7月[[2017年法国立法选举|法国立法选举]]前夕，[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]]的一项调查透露国民阵线的三位候选人都认同大取代理念<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.francesoir.fr/politique-france/racisme-homophobie-ce-que-lon-trouve-sur-les-comptes-des-candidats-fn-front-national-buzzfeed-circonscriptions-xenophobie-legislatives-deputes-twitter-facebook-fachosphere|title=Racisme, homophobie: ce que l'on trouve sur les comptes des candidats FN|language=fr|trans-title=Racism, homophobia: what we find on the accounts of FN candidates|publisher=France-Soir|date=2017-06-06|access-date=2019-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708124044/http://www.francesoir.fr/politique-france/racisme-homophobie-ce-que-lon-trouve-sur-les-comptes-des-candidats-fn-front-national-buzzfeed-circonscriptions-xenophobie-legislatives-deputes-twitter-facebook-fachosphere|archive-date=2019-07-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。参议员{{tsl|en|Stéphane Ravier|斯蒂芬·拉维尔}}的私人助理主张大取代已经在法国开始<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lepoint.fr/elections-legislatives/legislatives-front-national-des-candidats-pas-si-presentables-06-06-2017-2133151_573.php|title=Législatives – Front national : des candidats pas si présentables...|language=fr|trans-title=Legislative – National Front: not so presentable candidates ...|work=Le Point|date=2017-06-08|access-date=2019-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708124042/https://www.lepoint.fr/elections-legislatives/legislatives-front-national-des-candidats-pas-si-presentables-06-06-2017-2133151_573.php|archive-date=2019-07-08|url-status=live}}</ref>，以一张附文“对白人种族灭绝说不”的金发女孩的图片进一步推广大取代理念，表示“要选[[國民聯盟_(法國)|国民联盟]]，不然就会被入侵”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://france3-regions.francetvinfo.fr/provence-alpes-cote-d-azur/fn-paca-propos-racistes-islamophobes-candidats-aux-elections-legislatives-1268215.html|title=Le FN en PACA : des propos à caractère raciste et islamophobe des candidats aux législatives|language=fr|trans-title=The FN in PACA: Racist and Islamophobic remarks from candidates for the legislative elections|publisher=France Info|date=2017-06-07|access-date=2019-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708124042/https://france3-regions.francetvinfo.fr/provence-alpes-cote-d-azur/fn-paca-propos-racistes-islamophobes-candidats-aux-elections-legislatives-1268215.html|archive-date=2019-07-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。

2018年9月，在[[弗雷瑞斯|弗雷瑞斯]]的一场会议中，勒庞密切呼应大取代理念，表示“人类历史上从未有社会像法国这样组织不可逆转的取代运动”，认为取代运动会“稀释、取代（法国社会的）文化或生活方式”，从而让法国社会消失<ref name="Identity politics"/>。{{tsl|en|Le Pen family|勒庞家族}}的年轻成员、前[[國民議會_(法國)|国民议会]]代表[[玛丽昂·马雷夏尔-勒庞|玛丽昂·马雷夏尔-勒庞]]也支持取代理论<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.politico.eu/article/the-notre-dame-wildfire-that-cant-be-put-out/|title=The Notre Dame wildfire that can't be put out|website=Politico|date=2019-04-22|quote=Marion Maréchal—pegged as the heir apparent to the Le Pen dynasty and a possible presidential contender in 2022—is a proponent of the "Great Replacement" theory embraced by the man accused of the Christchurch killings in New Zealand.|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508171532/https://www.politico.eu/article/the-notre-dame-wildfire-that-cant-be-put-out/|archive-date=2019-05-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。2019年3月出访美国的时候，马雷夏尔表示自己“不希望法国变成伊斯兰教的土地”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.economist.com/europe/2019/03/14/meet-marion-marechal-the-next-voice-of-french-nationalism|title=Meet Marion Maréchal, the next voice of French nationalism|newspaper=The Economist|date=2019-03-14|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517155853/https://www.economist.com/europe/2019/03/14/meet-marion-marechal-the-next-voice-of-french-nationalism|archive-date=2019-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>，坚称大取代“不是子虚乌有”，认为土生法国人到2040年会变成少数民族，所以土生法国人现在想把“国家要回来”<ref name="heart of Europe's politics">{{cite news|url=https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/the-great-replacement-the-racist-idea-now-at-the-heart-of-europe-s-politics-20190319-p515cc.html|title='The Great Replacement': an idea now at the heart of Europe's politics|last1=Miller|first1=Nick|date=2019-03-19|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|access-date=2019-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331235005/https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/the-great-replacement-the-racist-idea-now-at-the-heart-of-europe-s-politics-20190319-p515cc.html|archive-date=2019-03-31|url-status=live}}</ref>。

马雷夏尔的姨妈、国民联盟党主席玛丽娜·勒庞笃信大取代理念。《[[法兰克福汇报|法兰克福汇报]]》直接称雷诺·加缪是勒庞的“教师爷”<ref name="Der Tag">{{cite news|url=https://www.tagesspiegel.de/kultur/anschlag-in-neuseeland-die-verschwoerungstheorie-des-todesschuetzen/24120366.html|title=Die Verschwörungstheorie des Todesschützen|language=de|trans-title=The Conspiracy Theory of the Gunner|newspaper=Der Tagesspiegel|date=2019-03-19|access-date=2019-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331225136/https://www.tagesspiegel.de/kultur/anschlag-in-neuseeland-die-verschwoerungstheorie-des-todesschuetzen/24120366.html|archive-date=2019-03-31|url-status=live}}</ref>。2019年5月，国民联盟发言人{{tsl|en|Jordan Bardella|约旦·巴尔德拉}}在与{{tsl|en|Nathalie Loiseau|娜塔莉·洛瓦索}}电视辩论时提到了大取代理论，认为法国必须果断采取措施阻挡非洲移民的{{tsl|en|demographic bomb|人口炸弹}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.francesoir.fr/politique-france/jordan-bardella-evoque-le-grand-remplacement-sans-le-nommer|title=Jordan Bardella évoque le "Grand remplacement" sans le nommer|language=fr|trans-title=Jordan Bardella evokes the "Great replacement" without naming it|publisher=France-Soir|date=2019-05-16|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517135252/http://www.francesoir.fr/politique-france/jordan-bardella-evoque-le-grand-remplacement-sans-le-nommer|archive-date=2019-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>。

