 Adam|date=2018-11-08|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190418151743/https://www.weeklystandard.com/adam-rubenstein/iowas-steve-king-takes-the-low-road-to-re-election|archive-date=2019-04-18|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/jewish-insider-s-daily-kickoff-november-9-2018-1.6636818|title=Jewish Insider's Daily Kickoff: November 9, 2018|website=Haaretz|date=2018-11-09|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130134759/https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/jewish-insider-s-daily-kickoff-november-9-2018-1.6636818|archive-date=2018-11-30|url-status=live}}</ref>。2019年[[基督城清真寺槍擊案|基督城清真寺槍擊案]]发生后，Vice指控戈尔迪经常鼓吹出生率下降、白人人口被取代的论调，而这两者都出现在凶手的“大取代”宣言中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vice.com/en_au/article/zma5a8/accused-new-zealand-shooter-had-canadian-mass-murderers-name-on-weapon|title=Accused New Zealand Shooter Had Canadian Mass Murderer's Name On Weapon|website=Vice Media|date=2019-03-15|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331025249/https://www.vice.com/en_au/article/zma5a8/accused-new-zealand-shooter-had-canadian-mass-murderers-name-on-weapon|archive-date=2019-03-31|url-status=live}}</ref>。忠实白人至上主义者{{tsl|en|Paul Fromm (white supremacist)|保罗·弗洛姆}}认为1967年前加拿大采用的[[加拿大红船旗|红船旗]]才能代表真正的加拿大欧洲加拿大，因为1965年出台的移民政策推动了叛国的取代欧洲人计划<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://nationalpost.com/news/canada/former-canadian-flag-the-red-ensign-gets-new-darker-life-as-far-right-symbol/wcm/80779f2c-6c23-4000-9917-85176a40e684|title=Former Canadian flag, the Red Ensign, gets new, darker life as far-right symbol|last=Hamilton|first=Graeme|work=National Post|access-date=2019-06-10|date=2017-07-10}}{{Dead link|date=November 2021 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

