====美国====
2017年，美国白人至上主义群体在[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]][[夏洛蒂镇|夏洛蒂镇]]举行[[2017年团结右翼集会|团结右翼集会]]，打出隐喻种族取代的标语{{sfnp|Bergmann|2018|p=127}}，譬如“你们不会取代我们”（You will not replace us）、“犹太人不能取代我们”（Jews will not replace us）<ref name="Bromley">{{cite journal |last=Bromley |first=Roger |title=The politics of displacement: the Far Right narrative of Europe and its 'others' |journal=From the European South |year=2018 |volume=3 |pages=13–26 |url=http://europeansouth.postcolonialitalia.it/journal/2018-3/2.Bromley.pdf |issn=2531-4130 |quote=[T]he 'Unite the Right', white nationalist, neo-fascist rally chanted 'you will not replace us' and 'the Jews will not replace us,' echoing the  'Great Replacement' claim, with a sharper anti-Semitic edge than is currently deployed publicly in Europe. |access-date=2019-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323180308/http://europeansouth.postcolonialitalia.it/journal/2018-3/2.Bromley.pdf |archive-date=2019-03-23 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name="foreign_affairs">{{cite journal|last1=Weitzmann|first1=Marc|title=The Global Language of Hatred Is French|journal=Foreign Affairs|date=2019-04-01|access-date=2019-04-03|url=https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/new-zealand/2019-04-01/global-language-hatred-french|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403005023/https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/new-zealand/2019-04-01/global-language-hatred-french|archive-date=2019-04-03|url-status=live}}</ref>。活动上，加缪向[[Vox|Vox]]明确表示不支持暴力行为，否认自己的思想与新纳粹分子有关联。不过，他认同这些口号背后的意义<ref name="Wildman"/>。

2018年10月，共和党国会议员[[史提夫·金|史提夫·金]]公开支持大取代理论<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2019/01/10/steve-king-white-supremacy/|title='I Am Simply a Nationalist.' Rep. Steve King Responds to Backlash Over 'White Supremacy' Remarks|website=Fortune|date=2019-01-10|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517165508/http://fortune.com/2019/01/10/steve-king-white-supremacy/|archive-date=2019-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newsweek.com/steve-king-white-society-superior-new-zealand-manifesto-1369162|title=Steve King Asked If White Society Is Superior to Nonwhite: 'I Don't Have an Answer for That'|website=Newsweek|date=2019-03-20|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517170506/https://www.newsweek.com/steve-king-white-society-superior-new-zealand-manifesto-1369162|archive-date=2019-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>，表示“没错，大取代正在发生”（Great replacement, yes），“通过[[欧洲移民危机|种族移民]]进入欧洲的人有80%是年轻人”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/10/us/politics/steve-king-trump-immigration-wall.html|title=Before Trump, Steve King Set the Agenda for the Wall and Anti-Immigrant Politics|website=The New York Times|date=2019-01-10|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190110172154/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/10/us/politics/steve-king-trump-immigration-wall.html|archive-date=2019-01-10|url-status=live}}</ref>。他认为大取代是欧洲和美国共同关心的问题，“如果我们继续把自己的孩子打掉，用年轻暴力的人取代他们，我们就是在换掉我们的文化、我们的文明”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/oct/26/hes-so-openly-racist-why-does-iowa-keep-electing-steve-king-to-congress|title='He's so openly racist': why does Iowa keep electing Steve King to Congress?|website=The Guardian|date=2018-10-27|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517070133/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/oct/26/hes-so-openly-racist-why-does-iowa-keep-electing-steve-king-to-congress|archive-date=2019-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>。他批评[[乔治·索罗斯|乔治·索罗斯]]就是大取代的罪魁祸首<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2019/01/steve-king-long-history-racist-comments-house-resolution/|title=Steve King Was Saying Insanely Racist Things Long Before Republicans Decided Enough Was Enough|website=Mother Jones|date=2019-01-15|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517030608/https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2019/01/steve-king-long-history-racist-comments-house-resolution/|archive-date=2019-05-17|url-status=live}}</ref>。

