y theory takes hold in Maine GOP |url=https://www.pressherald.com/2019/06/23/greg-kesich-conspiracy-theory-takes-hold-in-maine-gop/ |access-date=2019-10-07 |work=Portland Press Herald |date=2019-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007182205/https://www.pressherald.com/2019/06/23/greg-kesich-conspiracy-theory-takes-hold-in-maine-gop/ |archive-date=2019-10-07 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

2019年8月，极右翼恐怖分子在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[埃尔帕索_(德克萨斯州)|埃尔帕索]]一家[[沃尔玛|沃尔玛]]超市[[2019年埃尔帕索枪击案|开枪打死]]23名[[拉丁裔美国人|拉丁裔美国人]]，是美国现代史上拉丁裔美国人死亡最多的事件<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-49226573 |title=Texas Walmart shooting: El Paso attack 'domestic terrorism' |date=2019-08-05 |work=BBC News |access-date=2019-08-04 |archive-date=2019-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804124214/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-49226573 }}</ref><ref name="Romero">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/03/us/el-paso-walmart-shooting.html |title=Day at a Shopping Center in Texas Turns Deadly |last1=Romero |first1=Simon |last2=Fernandez |first2=Manny |last3=Padilla |first3=Mariel |date=2019-08-03 |work=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |url-access=limited |accessdate=2022-05-24 |archive-date=2019-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804043044/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/03/us/el-paso-walmart-shooting.html }}</ref>。案发前，枪手发布一段反拉丁裔、反移民宣言，推广大取代理论<ref name="Arango">{{cite news |last1=Arango |first1=Tim |last2=Bogel-Burroughs |first2=Nicholas |last3=Benner |first3=Katie |title=Minutes Before El Paso Killing, Hate-Filled Manifesto Appears Online |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/03/us/patrick-crusius-el-paso-shooter-manifesto.html |access-date=2019-08-04 |date=2019-08-03 |work=The New York Times |url-access=limited |archive-date=2019-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190917202031/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/03/us/patrick-crusius-el-paso-shooter-manifesto.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Fisher |first=Marc |title=A weekend of mass murder reflects how American violence goes viral |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2019-08-05 |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/a-weekend-of-mass-murder-reflects-how-american-violence-goes-viral/2019/08/04/d2ecfa3a-b6d7-11e9-b3b4-2bb69e8c4e39_story.html |url-access=limited |accessdate=2022-05-24 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129151719/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/a-weekend-of-mass-murder-reflects-how-american-violence-goes-viral/2019/08/04/d2ecfa3a-b6d7-11e9-b3b4-2bb69e8c4e39_story.html }}</ref>。宣言题为《难以忽视的真相》（The Incovenient Truth），共2300字，模仿{{tsl|en|immigration policy of Donald Trump|特朗普移民政策|美国总统唐纳德·特朗普}}的语言形容移民政策，将西班牙裔美国人形容为侵略者，扬言“把他们送回去”<ref name="Biesecker">{{cite news |last1=Biesecker |first1=Michael |last2=Dunklin |first2=Reese |last3=Kunzelman |first3=Michael |title=El Paso suspect appears to have posted anti-immigrant screed |url=https://apnews.com/df6dc60f37664833ba3b953927ef835d |agency=Associated Press |date=2019-08-04 |accessdate=2022-05-24 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203060338/https://apnews.com/df6dc60f37664833ba3b953927ef835d }}</ref>，同时让大家警惕“西班牙裔入侵德克萨斯州”<ref name="Rucker">{{cite news |last=Rucker |first=Philip |title='How do you stop these people?': Trump's anti-immigrant rhetoric looms over El Paso massacre |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/how-do-you-stop-these-people-trumps-anti-immigrant-rhetoric-looms-over-el-paso-massacre/2019/08/04/62d0435a-b6ce-11e9-a091-6a96e67d9cce_story.html |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2019-08-04 |url-access=limited |accessdate=2022-05-24 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127205647/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/how-do-you-stop-these-people-trumps-anti-immigrant-rhetoric-looms-over-el-paso-massacre/2019/08/04/62d0435a-b6ce-11e9-a091-6a96e67d9cce_story.html }}</ref>。

