 shooting anti-immigrant manifesto posted online |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/us/minutes-before-el-paso-shooting-anti-immigrant-manifesto-posted-online-1.3976819 |website=The Irish Times |accessdate=2022-05-26 |date=2019-08-04 |archive-date=2019-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804113938/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/us/minutes-before-el-paso-shooting-anti-immigrant-manifesto-posted-online-1.3976819 }}</ref>。

